    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically robust example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies. The powertrain is paired with a precise 6-speed manual transmission and a factory variable M differential lock. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity under high torque loads. The suspension has been refreshed with Bilstein dampers and poly-bushings, maintaining the sharp turn-in and communicative chassis dynamics this platform is known for. An honest, driver-focused machine with excellent mechanical provenance.",
