      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it's been such a great car for me. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014runs smoothly and has been well-loved over the years. There are a few minor signs of use here and there, as you'd expect, but nothing that takes away from how great it looks and feels on the road. It's the perfect reliable daily driver with plenty of adventures left in it. I'd love for it to go to a good home, so come take it for a spin!",
