      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound E46 M3, a quintessential analog driver\u2019s car. At its heart is the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that has been professionally overhauled for timing precision. This example features the desirable 6-speed longitudinal manual gearbox paired with a factory limited-slip differential, ensuring tactile engagement and predictable power delivery. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a reinforced rear subframe\u2014a critical upgrade for this platform\u2014and refreshed suspension bushings to maintain its signature handling geometry. While the exterior shows minor road wear consistent with spirited use, the drivetrain is robust and the engine pulls cleanly to its 8,000 RPM redline. This is a turn-key performance machine for the purist who values mechanical pedigree over garage-queen status.",
